snippet.title: Madou Run: a Game Made by Disc Station
snippet.description:
From Vol 19 of Disc Station and the only game that works. 
It's a racing like simulation, and it is based on the characters from the Puyo Puyo series. There are only 4 of them: Arle, Schezo, Witch and the Fish Dude(I'm calling him that cause why not). I tried grinding my opponents with power ups to win. This was released in 1998.
